Your use of `null` layouts is going to cause you no end of issues.  I&#39;d highly recommend you make the time to better understand the layout API and make use of it. See [Laying Out Components Within a Container](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/layout/index.html) for more details

